channel.title: What's your IQ?
channel.description:
Very simple and easy to determined, so simply click on this links and complete the following questions (please don't use google for this try to stick with mental math) and post your following sorces. Note- you can take a picture and post here aswell. Note- you could also ask questions and answers aswell.
[b]If You would LIKE to prove that you acutally got an high answer please TAKE a PIC[/b]
http://web.tickle.com/tests/uiqflash/
or
http://www.funeducation.com/Products/IQTest/intro.asp?source=Google&country=Canada
[hr] [b] Timers[/b]
http://www.iqtestforfree.com/
http://www.iqtest.com/prep.html
[hr]
Hard IQ test
http://www.highiqsociety.org/iq_tests/

item.title: What's your IQ?
item.dc:creator: @swordskid61 Swordskid61
item.description:
@swordskid61 wrote:

[quote=“r4ndom1, post:61, topic:146402”][quote author=Swordskid61 link=topic=200432.msg1784207#msg1784207 date=1190923618]

These IQ tests are about as accurate as the lies people post for scores.
If you want to do a real one, go to the Mensa website, send off for a free one, if you get 132+ they invite you to a supervised test and then if your score, again is in the top 2% in the world you’ll be invited to join Mensa as a member.

I know because I did it 6~ months ago. Most online tests are utter bullshit ones, not correctly constructed and often completely inaccurate. I once did an online test and was given the result “94” when my actualy IQ is in the region of 140.

i took one for a placemnet last year in the 8th grade do school placement tests lie?
[/quote]

as i said earlier the whole iq idea is a lie it is the measure of how good you are at iq tests and that is all. Why do you do an iq test to see what school you are in? surely that goes against everything iq pretends to be, if iq is an unlearnable thing which is a true measure of your intelligence why are you using that to pick which high school/groups you are in? Surely a test of the individual subjects would be more apt?[/quote]
truthfully, it doesnt matter to me what My IQ is anyway, all humans have to capacity to learn more and more.

I CAN agree with you though

Read full topic
